parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt buckle can lead to inadequate restraint in the event of an accident, increasing the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The seat belt buckle fails to fasten properly
the buckle unsnaps when going over bumpy roads
the middle seat belt does not lock at all
the driver's side seat belt and rear passenger side belt do not work properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Delayed or refused recall repairs can lead to continued use of a defective seat belt system, increasing the risk of injury or fatality in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Dealership refuses to rectify the problem
parts are not available
no response from the manufacturer or dealership
recall repairs refused due to lack of paperwork.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: An electrical system fire can cause significant damage to the vehicle and its contents, and can potentially lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Unexplained fire in the vehicle
intense heat
melting of components
destruction of personal belongings.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: Transmission popping out of gear
unusual noise from the rear end
difficulty shifting gears.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Differential failure can cause loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: Unusual noise from the rear end
vibration while driving
difficulty maintaining speed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Cracking of the frame rail can compromise the structural integrity of the vehicle, potentially leading to loss of control, accidents, or injuries.
symptoms: Cracking or breaking of the frame rail
pulling away of the steel from the seat
loose or detached seat anchors.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Loose or detached front seat track anchors can cause the seat to shift or become unstable during driving, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Loose or detached seat anchors
bolts coming out
seat instability or shifting while driving.
